Using data which we have, to attract people go from Free plan to Premium plan, we can: 

● Promote more relaxation playlists in Spotify advertisement

● Promote the playlists at night, as the activity is highest during the night time 

● It will be more beneficial to promote 1-3 months no charge subscription for those who have used the Spotify app for over a year, so they can experience the difference 

● For enhanced listener satisfaction, diversify podcast content and keep durations concise, catering to the preference for shorter episodes among many users 
